This is the best cam vid that I've ever seen actually, video wise lol.  It gets dark in a couple of spots, but not to a point where you can't see.  The audio isn't bad.  You can tell that it's in a theater, but it's no different than if you set your radio equalizer to hall.  You can still hear it clearly though.  Overall, an excellent copy.  A/6 V/9
